# TEMPORARY (2026-07-22): transport of the orchestrator store to another machine.
# The three lines below re-include ONLY .plan/local/orchestrator/ through the
# excluded parent (.plan/* excludes .plan/local, so a lone negation would be dead —
# git never descends into an excluded directory). REMOVE this block after the
# transfer lands on the target machine.
!.plan/local/
.plan/local/*
!.plan/local/orchestrator/
